# Univocity: use mise for python, task, uv, slither, foundry.
# Only this directory uses mise; your global pyenv (in ~/.bashrc) is unchanged.
# When you cd here, direnv runs this and prepends mise's tools to PATH, so
# `python`, `task`, `uv`, `forge`, `slither` come from mise. Outside this
# directory, pyenv remains in effect.
#
# Optional: inherit parent (forestrie) env vars (e.g. SHARED_AGENT_DOCS).
# Uncomment the next line if you need them; then PYENV_VERSION may be set
# but mise's python still wins because mise's PATH is prepended.
source_up_if_exists
use mise
